<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Rebel Wilson is currently back in Los Angeles and she made sure to stop in to her favourite hair stylist to get her quarrantine hair tended to. </p>

<p>The actress dropped by to visit her best friend, celebrity hair cutter and colourist Nicole Leal, to update her blonde locks. </p>

<p>Showing off the results of the neat new cut in a mirror selfie shared to Instagram Stories, the 40-year-old also flaunted her incredible weight loss. </p>

<p>Looking good! Rebel Wilson (pictured) showed off the results of her weight loss in a mirror selfie shared to Instagram Stories on Friday </p>

<p>Rebel looked sensational in a frilly black blouse and fitted skirt that fit perfectly to her trim physique. </p>

<p>The top featured scalloped sleeves and a peplum design, sitting beautifully over the pencil skirt, with Rebel adding a thin belt to ensemble. </p>

<p>She poked her tongue out in the mirror, her prominent cheekbones and slimmed down features evident. </p>

<p>New do! Rebel is back in Los Angeles and dropped by to visit her best friend, celebrity hair cutter and colourist Nicole Leal, to update her blonde locks</p>

<p>Looking good: In another selfie shared to Instagram, Rebel showed off just her face</p>

<p>The Isn't It Romantic actress wrote in her caption: 'Finishing touch - perfume... but which one?'</p>

<p>In another selfie shared to Instagram, Rebel showed off just her face as she rested upon her dressing table, and mused that she needed a spritz of scent for her outfit. </p>

<p>The Isn't It Romantic actress wrote in the caption: 'Finishing touch - perfume... but which one?' </p>

<p>Rebel  has been on a health and fitness journey so far this year, losing at least 18kg (40lbs or 2.8 stone).   </p>

<p>Last month, Rebel updated fans on her weight loss journey by sharing several photos to Instagram of herself looking slimmer in a tight blue dress.</p>

<p>Wow! Last month, Rebel updated fans on her weight loss journey by sharing photos to Instagram of herself looking slimmer in a tight blue dress (left). Right: Rebel in May 2019</p>

<p>The Bridesmaids star explained in the caption that she was inching closer and closer to her goal weight of 75kg (165lbs, or 11.8 stone).</p>

<p>'Thanks for all the love so far on my "Year of Health" journey,' she told her followers.</p>

<p>'When I was reaching for the candies last night after dinner I thought to myself 'hmmmm...better not' and had a bottle of water instead.'</p>

<p>'Eight kilos to go until I hit my goal. Hopefully I can do it by the end of the year.'</p>

<p>'Year of health': Rebel announced in January that she was going to make her health a priority in 2020. Pictured on August 16</p>
